entries.femaleVariant: Gah, fuck!
What a performance, huh? Know what it was about?
Jesus... the fuck do you want from me?
It's all goin' too slow.
You don't care if I live.
Still don't see how Mikoshi's linked to my chip problem.
Not the brightest bulb on stage, are ya?
What do Soulkiller and Mikoshi have to do with me?
Leave me alone.
Wanted me dead, said so yourself.
Made it pretty clear since that I changed my mind. Want you to live now.
Asked you already... what the hell ya want from me?
See, me and Arasaka, we got a half-century-old score needs settling, and I plan to do it.
Gonna make a terrorist of me?
Funny guy.
Never been recruited into a terrorist cell before. Feel kinda honored, actually.
Listen, I know things, where we can save your life, who can help us do that.
You'll get rid of the chip, I'll smash 'Saka – win-win, kid.
It's honestly as if you were tryin' to make exactly no sense.
Soulkiller's what we need and Mikoshi's how we grab it.
Mikoshi – what's that, exactly?
But I don't trust you.
You're just a hallucination.
You know you're just an irritating hallucination, right? Should just ignore you.
And you're a walkin' corpse. Should just wait till your mind shrivels to nothing and frees up space for me.
OK, so, this Mikoshi – what is it, exactly?
Don't trust you – clear, right? So why would I trust in your plan?
'Cause you've heard your death knell but you'd rather live.
So if you're done bitchin', I'd be happy to explain – sound good?
Mikoshi – what's that, exactly?
Not particularly.
Not really, no.
I got a get-outta-jail-free card. I'd be a fuckin' fool not to take advantage.
OK, basics. If you're jacked in, cruisin' the Net, Arasaka can use Soulkiller, an AI, to trap, fry and pack away your psyche, your mind and your soul.
Followin' so far?
Yeah, seen the memories – did a real number on ya.
OK... Seems we got a few more things to broach than I thought, but that'll come later.
Anyway, when Soulkiller fries, roasts and boils you, you die. But the contents of your mind get copied to an engram first.
Sure. That's how you became a construct.
Exactly. Now, Mikoshi's the place Soulkiller operates out of, where it stores its victims' engrams.
Me and Mikoshi – how're we linked at all?
Cut to the chase.
C'mon, c'mon – you got more to say, so just say it.
And, uh, how you plan to smash Arasaka this time? Got another nuke tucked away?
Fifty years back, ops on the human mind – Mikoshi was the sole place on Earth where they did anything like that.
Bet it still is today. Tellin' ya, all roads lead there. It's where we'll settle our biz – you yours, me mine.
Leave me alone.
Can't find the words to describe exactly how fucked up you are.
I just needed a calmer moment to think. And yeah, figured since fate gave me another shot, I'll take it.
To live life to the fullest? See the northern lights, run with the mechbulls or with gazelles on a safari?
To finish what I started. I'm back in the game. Want 'Saka out, so I'm gonna need you in.
Might even laugh if it didn't hurt so much.
Arasaka – how you plan to destroy it this time?
Distracting you. That was Hanako Arasaka, attemptin' to--
W-what's goin' on?
So, you found Hellman and got what to show for it? Empty promises.
Ah, fuck...!
Ugh, the hell's that?
Well, sooner or later, Mikoshi's where we're headed.
Already got my plan, thanks. And I'm gonna stick to it.
Tellin' ya, sooner or later, Mikoshi's where we're headed.
Asked you – what the hell do you want?
Fucked in the head worse than me.
For some ideal? Or to square a grudge?
But why? Fightin' for some dated ideal? Pursuin' a personal vendetta?
Ravings of a lunatic.
Following.
Don't care.
Yep, saw what happened to you.
Agh, fuck!
[Sit] Dunno.
[Sit]
Aghh... Not sure...
Ugh... No idea...
Hell's wrong with you?
Still wanna find Parker, shape you're in?
Really think you'll find Hellman or Parker, condition you're in?
To croak in the shadow of some megablock?
To sell yourself to the 'Sakas? They'll end you, plain as that.
To croak outside some flea-ridden motel?
You don't need to know. Here to get me from point A to point B.
This time bomb's named Alt Cunningham.
Not yet. But you will once we find what we need.
Enough to know this is bullshit.
For now, we got no time to lose, need to get inside Mikoshi.
You fuckin' asshole…
But as should be obvious, I've decided to help you. Need to find somethin' first – seven letters, starts with an M…
[Stand] OK, talked enough.
Feelin' a bit better now, so scram. Got somethin' important needs doin'.
One last thing. Alt Cunningham – she's the ace up my sleeve.
Oh, fuck off. Tired of hearing your voice.
entries.maleVariant: Oh, fuck off. I'm tired of hearing your voice.

entries.femaleVariant: Don't blame ya, but you'll hear me yet. And don't get killed in the meantime, will ya?
I'm s'posed to know who that is?
Gonna decomish before we learn how to rip the chip out.
That's what I need you for.
No, no, dammit!
What the fuck you gawkin' at?
Whaddaya want?!
Fuck off, not your biz.
Man, if I only had some heat in my hand…
The fuck--?!
[Stand]
What do you want from me?
